---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Bostrich"
  description="We're on a mission to democratize access to enterprise-grade solutions. Learn about our vision and values."
>
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Our Mission
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We believe every organization deserves access to solutions that help them grow, adapt, and succeed. That's why we've dedicated ourselves to building infrastructure that scales with your ambitions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Story Section -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-4">
        <p>
          Bostrich was founded on a simple observation: too many organizations struggle with the fundamental challenge of reaching the next level. Whether scaling operations, transitioning leadership, or executing a strategic exit, the tools available were either too complex, too expensive, or simply didn't exist.
        </p>
        <p>
          We set out to change that. Our team of industry veterans came together with a shared vision: democratize access to the solutions that have traditionally been reserved for the largest enterprises. Today, organizations of all sizes trust Bostrich to support their most critical growth and transition initiatives.
        </p>
        <p>
          From our headquarters in Boston, we serve clients across 47 countries, helping them navigate the challenges of scaling, transitioning, and thriving in an ever-changing business landscape.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Our Values</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Reliability</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">When it matters most, you can count on us. Our solutions are built to perform under pressure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Simplicity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Complex problems deserve elegant solutions. We believe in doing one thing exceptionally well.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Integrity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We stand behind our products and our promises. No hidden fees, no surprises.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Leadership</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Our leadership team brings decades of combined experience in enterprise solutions, operations, and strategic growth.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block text-indigo-600 font-semibold hover:text-indigo-700 transition-colors">
        Get in Touch →
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
